item.name: Screen Printing
item.desc:
Please note that all of our products listed on our site will be screen printed unless otherwise specified. We recommend that you keep your camera ready artwork down to a limit of one color per front and back to keep the cost of the product low. If you have any questions, feel free to contact us.
Please note that color printed may vary from what your custom rendition shows due to your computers screen resolution settings. We aim to provide you with the closest possible replication of what you have created on our site. Thanks.

start.dtext: Choose the style and font, add color, shape and curve. Text-It your way.
start.dgallery: Drag and drop or doubleclick to place image on your lacrosse pinnies.
start.dupload: Create your own unique design. Remember the quality of the upload will affect the final product. We recommend that you use a .png or .gif for best view.
start.letus: Fill out our brief info page here and one of our agents will contact you in the next 24 hours with a Mockup/Quote
start.retnames: This design contains custom NAME and/or NUMBER aliases (with text EXAMPLE or 00). To edit your team list, please click on the Names and Numbers link on the bottom left hand corner of this page above the FACEBOOK icon. You do not need Names/Numbers to complete your order. If no names or numbers are selected, choose the shopping cart image in the middle of the page.

letuswiz.selectproduct: Please select a color for your lacrosse pinnies, if you need to change the product, please close this window and go to our product catalog at the left panel, select needed product and open this window again.
letuswiz.frontdesign: Here you can upload your own logo, enter text and make a notes for front and back side design of your lacrosse pinnies.
letuswiz.finish: Please, enter your contact information and additional notes for our staff. Please be as descriptive as possible so that we may better assist you.
